item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: weskhaled
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Our website address is: http://dynamix.develop.

What personal data we collect and why we collect it

Comments

When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.

An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.

Media

If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.

Contact forms

Cookies

If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.

If you have an account and you log in to this site, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select "Remember Me", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.

If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.

Embedded content from other websites

Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.

These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.

Analytics

Who we share your data with

How long we retain your data

If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.

What rights you have over your data

If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

Where we send your data

Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.

Your contact information

Additional information

How we protect your data

What data breach procedures we have in place

What third parties we receive data from

What automated decision making and/or profiling we do with user data

Industry regulatory disclosure requirements

item.title: Why choose us
item.dc:creator: weskhaled
item.content:encoded:
Join our team

A career with Dynamix is one that will harness and develop the innovative and well-experienced IT professional. We have an extensive recruitment experience with finding the best resourceful and high-energy individuals who are poised for growth and success.

Our comprehensive benefits programs are well-balanced in terms of being locally competitive and customizable to the individual employee and family needs

We maintain a comprehensive, competitive benefits program that address the health, welfare and security of our employees, they are designed with flexibility that facilitates selection according to employees, specific needs and circumstances.

Why join Dynamix?

  • We provide a long term employment contract (CDI) to our consultants and we keep on following their career progress: Regular follow-up of each project on which works each consultant, and intervention in case of problems.
  • An attractive salary package and other extra-legal bonuses and vouchers. The NET remuneration is 25% to 40% higher than the Belgian average for computer scientists.
  • Many incentives and possibilities of evolution as a team leader or in a technical field of your choice: our consultants are changing projects to move forward, learn new technologies, and take on greater tasks.
  • Our consultants work in various sectors of activity: banks (BNP Paribas), insurance, European Commission, European Parliament, Belgian Government, public organizations, startups, mutual health, space agencies (Spacebel), public Transport, Pharmaceutical and chemistry (Bayer)
  • Continuous trainings in IT to boost skills with cutting-edge technologies(Angular 2/4, js, mango db node, js, DevOps, Groovy, Java 8, GIT, express…)
  • The recruitment process, the conduct of interviews and the final decision are made quickly.
  • Diversity: you will work in a multicultural environment (our consultants are from multiple nationalities: Indian, Moroccan, Tunisian, Russian…) which will improve the communication, the openness, the tolerance and curiosity.
  • Our priority: Quality is better than quantity, because Dynamix has a good reputation in the marketplace because we believe that Our people are our brand.
  • In case you’re not a resident in Belgium or in the EU and you want to join our team for a new challenging experience: Dynamix will assist you to find your first accommodation, we help our new hires to find their first housing. If necessary, Dynamix will pay the two months of security deposit and the first month’s rent, this amount will be deducted the salary at the rate of 300 euros per month.

Why work in Belgium?

  • The delay to receive the work permit is up to one month.
  • Quick family reunification process (it takes 4 to 6 months). The employee can even apply for a visa for his family before his arrival in Belgium. In France it takes 2 and a half years for family reunification
  • Housing in Brussels is of quality, available and not expensive (2 to 3 times cheaper than in Paris)
  • Medical coverage (medical visits, medication, reimbursement of up to 100% of hospitalization)

Do you want to push your career to the next level and to work in a place where you can be inspired and be inspiring? If so, Dynamix is the best place to be, because we believe that our success is mainly due to our human capital, we aim to bring together all human resources of Dynamix in our business project. So! Embrace yourself and Join US!

item.title: CONTACT US
item.dc:creator: weskhaled
item.content:encoded:
DynamiX s.a is a Management company of Java consultants. We are specialized in Java web Development, the Java consulting team at DynamiX s.a is proficient and experienced to create and manage applications aptly and accordingly adapted with the fast changing technological advancements. Our consultants are equipped to work on existing applications and transform them to meet your future business objectives and expectations

DynamiX s.a is specialized in finding high level profiles from Tunisia, Morocco and India and to obtain for them the Belgian work permit. Our network of consultants ensures the responsiveness, technical skills, strategic dimension and human skills you need. DynamiX s.a , focuses on the values that will allow it to create a lasting relationship with its customers: the pugnacity, fidelity and human qualities

Mission Statement

Expertise

Because expertise is a prerequisite, the consultant Dynamix SA shares a vision where the consultant is able to do and say the right thing in any social situation. He has the ability to ensure high performance, adaptive capacity and understanding of issues, to make sure of the success of our mission.

Accountability and trust

Holding people accountable is a fundamental proof of good management. Aware of the strategic issues in the missions entrusted to him, the Dynamix consultant acts loyally and ethically

Responsibility

Respect of the commitments made towards the customer. Quality and clarity of communication are important keyroles to the achievement of their goals.

Management Vision

Dynamix s.a is a team of dedicated and passionate professionals with more than 16 years of experience in Java Resourcing. Dynamix s.a was founded with the mission to serve the growth and the needs of our customers across the world by providing the quality Java Staff resourcing

– Number one choice for its customers

– Having Happy & Talented employees in a team

– Market Leader in Java Staff resourcing

Dynamix s.a believes that our employees are our true strength and that we together will help our customers to achieve their corporate objectives

Dynamix s.a is a customer oriented company focusing on building long-lasting partnerships with our clients to achieve mutual success

Dynamix s.a’s IT Staff resourcing services are primarily focused on Java/J2EE and web development

item.title: Careers
item.dc:creator: weskhaled
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]

Join our team

A career with Dynamix s.a is one that will harness and develop the innovative and well-experienced IT professional. We are looking for resourceful and high-energy individuals who are poised for growth and success

Job Application Process

  • The organization of the technical interviews is done very quickly
  • The decision process is very short
  • The process for obtaining a work permit takes three weeks
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]

Opportunities

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_separator el_width="40"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]

JAVA Developer

Are you a passionate JAVA Developer? You are looking for your new challenge? Then join us and let us help you unleash your talent. We are a dynamic company specialized in IT services, based in Brussels. Dynamix is growing rapidly with huge potential for skills and projects in various sectors combining IT expertise and knowledge of business processes. The ideal candidate will be an enthusiastic developer eager to learn and grow his/her skills in the field. Your Position:
  • Participate in design discussions, and translate business requirements into technical tasks.
  • Contribute in all phases of the development lifecycle
  • Plan and execute all deployment of system features and monitor for successful integration, maintaining the system throughout its lifecycle
  • Conduct the testing of completed code modules, fixing code as needed to ensure a smooth system deployment with the intended functionality
  • You will work mainly in: Java/ J2EE, HTML 5 / CSS 3, JavaScript, Angular JS, Spring, Hibernate
Your profile:
  • You graduated from an engineering school with a degree in computer sciences/software engineering
  • You have 5 years of real-world experience developing complex data-driven applications.
  • Strong background in HTML 5 / CSS 3, JavaScript, REST, Angular JS, JAVA, Spring, Hibernate, XML, HTML, AJAX and related technologies.
  • Practical experience of OO design and UML
  • Thorough understanding of relational databases such as MySQL or similar technologies.
  • Agile/Scrum development cycle understanding.
  • You are fluent in French and English
Our Offer:
  • You will work as a JAVA/JEE developer in Belgium and You will join a firm that put the human relations at the heart of its identity.
  • Long-term contract, a work permit, a residence permit, a family reunion…
  • An attractive salary package and other extra-legal benefits.
  • An international career and working within European projects.
If you are excited about using cutting-edge technology in a fast-paced work environment then apply today! Send us your recent CV to hanan@dynamix-it.be (Subject: Name, first name, age, number of years of experience. Body of mail: 5 lines to explain the meaning of your application.)[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]

item.title: candidates
item.dc:creator: weskhaled
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]

Join our team

[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]A career with Dynamix is one that will harness and develop the innovative and well-experienced IT professional. We have an extensive recruitment experience with finding the best resourceful and high-energy individuals who are poised for growth and success. Our comprehensive benefits programs are well-balanced in terms of being locally competitive and customizable to the individual employee and family needs. We maintain a comprehensive, competitive benefits program that address the health, welfare and security of our employees, they are designed with flexibility that facilitates selection according to employees’ specific needs and circumstances.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]

Why join Dynamix?

  • We provide a long term employment contract (CDI) to our consultants and we keep on following their career progress: Regular follow-up of each project on which works each consultant, and intervention in case of problems.
  • An attractive salary package and other extra-legal bonuses and vouchers. The NET remuneration is 25% to 40% higher than the Belgian average for computer scientists.
  • Many incentives and possibilities of evolution as a team leader or in a technical field of your choice: our consultants are changing projects to move forward, learn new technologies, and take on greater tasks.
  • Our consultants work in various sectors of activity: banks (BNP Paribas), insurance, European Commission, European Parliament, Belgian Government, public organizations, startups, mutual health, space agencies (Spacebel), public Transport, Pharmaceutical and chemistry (Bayer)
  • Continuous trainings in IT to boost skills with cutting-edge technologies(Angular 2/4, js, mango db node, js, DevOps, Groovy, Java 8, GIT, express…)
  • The recruitment process, the conduct of interviews and the final decision are made quickly.
  • Diversity: you will work in a multicultural environment (our consultants are from multiple nationalities: Indian, Moroccan, Tunisian, Russian…) which will improve the communication, the openness, the tolerance and curiosity.
  • Our priority: Quality is better than quantity, because Dynamix has a good reputation in the marketplace because we believe that Our people are our brand.
  • In case you’re not a resident in Belgium or in the EU and you want to join our team for a new challenging experience: Dynamix will assist you to find your first accommodation, we help our new hires to find their first housing. If necessary, Dynamix will pay the two months of security deposit and the first month’s rent, this amount will be deducted the salary at the rate of 300 euros per month.
 

Why work in Belgium?

  • The delay to receive the work permit is up to one month.
  • Quick family reunification process (it takes 4 to 6 months). The employee can even apply for a visa for his family before his arrival in Belgium. In France it takes 2 and a half years for family reunification
  • Housing in Brussels is of quality, available and not expensive (2 to 3 times cheaper than in Paris)
  • Medical coverage (medical visits, medication, reimbursement of up to 100% of hospitalization)
Do you want to push your career to the next level and to work in a place where you can be inspired and be inspiring? If so, Dynamix is the best place to be, because we believe that our success is mainly due to our human capital, we aim to bring together all human resources of Dynamix in our business project. So! Embrace yourself and Join US![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]
